DISCLAIMER

The software TaxT provided herein is released as a prototype implementation on behalf of scientists and engineers working within the GEM (Global Earthquake Model) Foundation. It is distributed for the purpose of open collaboration and in the hope that is will be useful to the scientific, engineering and software design communities. 

The software is NOT distributed as part of the GEM OpenQuake suite (www.globalquakemodel.org/openquake) and must be considered as a separate entity. The software provided herein is designed and implemented by scientific staff. It is not developed to the design standards, nor subject to same level of critical review by professional software developers, as the GEM OpenQuake software suite.  

Feedback and contribution to the software is welcome, and can be directed to the scientific staff of the GEM Model Facility (www.globalquakemodel.org). 
